1. Scope

This license applies to the Howstudy guide corpus in this directory
(research/howstudy/): the origin documents (HS-ogn.md), the Korean edition
core excerpt (kor/), and the complete English edition (eng/).

This is a directory-level exception to the repository-wide content license
(CC BY 4.0 — see ../../LICENSE-CONTENT). The full Korean edition of this
guide is being prepared for commercial publication, so the corpus is
published under a non-commercial license.


